<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_505" id="252r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_505_r1l17">Otten Heẏden </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_505_r1l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Ott / Laſʒ niht / du ſeiſt auf den nehſten Montag frü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l19">cʒu Ratecʒeite hynnen bey vns / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etvvaʒ notlichs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l20">mit dir cʒu reden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das dıch ſelber antrifft / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l21"><expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Aſſu<ex>m</ex>pt<ex>ionis</ex></expan> . <expan>M<ex>arie</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_505" id="252r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Otten Heyden </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Ott, lasz niht, du seist <app><note><q type="date">auf den nehsten montag</q>22.08.1412</note></app> frü czu rateczeite hynnen bey uns, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        etwaz notlichs mit dir czu reden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> das dich
                        selber antrifft. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>assu<ex>m</ex>pt<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>M<ex>arie</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
